item.title: crabs are everywhere
item.description: I am going deep into a forest in Mumbai. Udhar people talk about folk tales of the animal that would not like to meet. Though no one has really seen it. Amidst all those scary tales and keeping our eyes open, I suddenly see what ? crabs. Crabs everywhere
